Description: **crawl_requests**
        ==================
        
        *Usage:*
        --------
        >>>import requests
        
        >>>from true_encoding.true_encoding import Tcode ##
        
        >>>res = requests.get('https://python.org')
        
        >>>res.encoding = Tcode(res) ##
        
        >>>content = res.text
        
